{"tid":2373343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[支國新聞] 春節返鄉需持7日內核酸陰性證明","createTime":"2021-01-20T11:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T11:29:33.000Z","uid":277572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a3027ea9ff0fd90b9ec333b149998a468174bb79","tid":2373343,"uid":277572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:25:07.000Z","msg":"國家衛健委疾控局監察專員王斌：全國各地要實行鄉採樣、縣檢測，檢測機構要在收到樣本後的12小時內反饋檢測結果；如果說一定要返鄉，返鄉人員需持有7日以內核酸檢測陰性證明才能夠返鄉，同時這些返鄉人員回去以後，當地基層政府要進行網格化管理。​​​​<br />\n<br />\n會後，王斌在回答第一財經採訪時表示，返鄉人群不分高中低風險區，費用自己承擔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMnZ3Q3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMnZ3Q3.png&h=76f2b7c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNqXQv3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNqXQv3.png&h=921d8622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haVwUXJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaVwUXJ.png&h=6e77e6d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bz8VCa3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbz8VCa3.png&h=72c2c7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKXOXa3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKXOXa3.png&h=2223cd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返鄉下 VS 大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789593b7361206c800ad7c9f7471a421ac79a1af","tid":2373343,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afxGxL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafxGxL0.jpg&h=6fba4260&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6adf65f8097bbcce4ddfb68e69ec20baa5579f0","tid":2373343,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g99d8js.jpg\" data-thumbna